<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width" />
  <title><%= @subject || 'DoubleDate' %></title>
  
  <style type="text/css">
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
  table tr#footer td p a:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

  @media only screen and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.3),
         only screen and (-o-min-device-pixel-ratio: 13/10),
         only screen and (min-resolution: 120dpi) {
    
    h1.logo {
      background-image: url(<%= image_path('email/upper-logo@2x.png') %>) !important;
      background-size: 44px 66px;
    }

    table#table-wrapper td.wrapper-nw {
      background-image: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-nw@2x.png') %>) !important;
      background-size: 30px 130px;
    }

    table#table-wrapper td.wrapper-ne {
      background-image: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-ne@2x.png') %>) !important;
      background-size: 30px 130px;
    }

    table#table-wrapper td.wrapper-sw {
      background-image: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-sw@2x.png') %>) !important;
      background-size: 30px 12px;
    }

    table#table-wrapper td.wrapper-se {
      background-image: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-se@2x.png') %>) !important;
      background-size: 30px 12px;
    }

    table#table-wrapper td.wrapper-s {
      background-image: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-s@2x.png') %>) !important;
      background-size: 1px 12px;
    }

    table tr#footer .footer-right {
      background-image: url(<%= image_path('email/text-logo@2x.png') %>) !important;
      background-size: 111px 19px;
    }
  }  

  @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) { 
    table[id=outer-wrapper] { 
      width: 300px !important;
    }

    table#table-wrapper td.wrapper-n h2 {
      margin-top: 10px !important;
      font-size: 34px !important;
    }

    table#table-wrapper td.wrapper-n h3 {
      font-size: 16px !important;
    }

    table tr#footer .footer-left,
    table tr#footer .footer-right {
      width: 100% !important;
      display: block !important;
      float: none !important;
      text-align: left !important;
      background-position: 0 50% !important;
    }
  }
  </style>
</head>

<body leftmargin="0" marginwidth="0" topmargin="0" marginheight="0" offset="0" style="background: #ff1178; font-family: HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
  <center>
    
    <table id="outer-wrapper" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" height="100%" width="100%" style="width: 80%; max-width: 680px; margin: 0;">
      <tr id="header">
        <td colspan="2" align="center" valign="top">
          <h1 class="logo" style="width: 44px; height: 66px; display: inline-block; background: url(<%= image_path('email/upper-logo.png') %>) 0 0 no-repeat; margin: 30px auto; text-indent: -9999em;"></h1>
        </td>
      </tr>
      
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2">
          <table id="table-wrapper" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" height="100%" width="100%">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <td class="wrapper-nw" width="30px" height="130px" style="background: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-nw.png') %>) top left no-repeat;"></td>
                <td class="wrapper-n" valign="top" style="background: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-n.png') %>) top left repeat-x; max-height: 130px; overflow: hidden; padding: 25px 0 0 0; text-shadow: 0 1px 0 #FFF;">
                  <h2 style="font-size: 48px; color: #ff1178; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</h2>
                  <h3 style="color: #7d7d7d; font-size: 20px; margin: 0;"><%= @subject %></h3>
                </td>
                <td class="wrapper-ne" width="30px" height="130px" style="background: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-ne.png') %>) top left no-repeat;"></td>
              </tr>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="wrapper-mid" colspan="3" style="padding: 20px 30px; background: #FFF; color: #444; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" background="#FFF">
                  <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;"><b><%= RegistrationEvent::coin_value %> coins</b> are already yours as a big thank you for giving DoubleDate a shot. Coins are used to start incoming chat messages from other users.</p>

                  <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;"><b>DoubleDate is about going out with your wing to meet two other people.</b> A wing can be your best friend, your boyfriend, girlfriend, a colleague from work, your husband or wife, or anyone with a pulse.</p>

                  <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;"><b>We're different.</b> Instead of sorting through profiles and surfing through pictures, our mission is to get you out in the real world to have fun. DoubleDate isn't about love and romance, it's about having a great time.</p>

                  <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;"><b>Explore DoubleDates</b> that are nearby in your area. Taking a trip? Filter things that users are doing on the other side of the world.</p>

                  <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;"><b>Create your own!</b> Have a couple of extra concert tickets? Planning a board game at your local coffee house? Maybe you were invited to a doubles badminton championship? You can post it on DoubleDate!</p>
                  
                  <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;"><b>Whats next?</b> We’ve worked really hard to bring DoubleDate to life and we think you’ll really enjoy it. We're constantly working on new ways to get you offline and out having fun. Expect some cool things from DoubleDate this summer, we've got a LOT in store for you!</p>

                  <p><cite>&mdash; Marcus &amp; Michael, Founders of DoubleDate</cite></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>

            <tfoot>
              <tr>
                <td class="wrapper-sw" height="12px" width="30px" style="background: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-sw.png') %>) 0 0 no-repeat;"></td>
                <td class="wrapper-s" height="12px" style="background: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-s.png') %>) 0 0 repeat-x;">&nbsp;</td>
                <td class="wrapper-se" height="12px" width="30px" style="background: url(<%= image_path('email/wrapper-se.png') %>) 0 0 no-repeat;"></td>
              </tr>
            </tfoot>
          </table>

        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr id="footer">
        <td colspan="2" style="padding: 10px 30px; color: #FFF; font-size: 13px;">
          <div class="footer-right" style="float: right; display: inline-block; width: 50%; display: block; height: 35px; background: url(<%= image_path('email/text-logo.png') %>) 100% 50% no-repeat;"></div>

          <div class="footer-left" style="float: left; display: inline-block; width: 50%;">
            <p style="line-height: 20px;">
              <b>&copy; 2013 DoubleDate</b> — <%= link_to 'dbld8.com', root_url, :style => "color: #FFF; text-decoration: none;" %><br/>
              <%= link_to 'Terms', static_url('terms'), :style => "color: #FFF; text-decoration: none;" %> •
              <%= link_to 'Privacy', static_url('privacy'), :style => "color: #FFF; text-decoration: none;" %> •
              <%= mail_to 'hello@dbld8.com', 'Contact Us', :style => "color: #FFF; text-decoration: none;" %>
            </p>
          </div>
          
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

  </center>
</body>
</html>